修讀有關AED（心臟去纖震器）的使用課程。"},{"pid":"b176092dbd6a7de80f3c148e20cca3a4a54b2296","tid":1031391,"uid":236401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:36:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"769d4829f74a6b6e333c85ed6e633e71b66be8dc","tid":1031391,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T20:19:46.000Z","msg":"乜嘢叫： 收下體照<span style=\"color: red;\">性電郵</span>？<br />\n就算拆做 <span style=\"color: violet;\">收下體照性</span> 電郵<br />\n都唔知嗡乜撚嘢！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa4da2b4e22c259d54999d570b08c807da2e09e","tid":1031391,"uid":2896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"769d4829f74a6b6e333c85ed6e633e71b66be8dc","tid":1031391,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T20:19:46.000Z","msg":"乜嘢叫： 收下體照<span style=\"color: red;\">性電郵</span>？<br />\n就算拆做 <span style=\"color: violet;\">收下體照性</span> 電郵<br />\n都唔知嗡乜撚嘢！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T20:25:11.000Z","msg":"應該係中文垃圾到直譯sex mail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da927356f21f8a98ef0cfe95f0b915e43d9b225","tid":1031391,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T21:24:06.000Z","msg":"個老公到死都唔知啦 算幸福"},{"pid":"efe0cdb6c577829835319e0659955bc988e6fa6d","tid":1031391,"uid":59511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T21:56:58.000Z","msg":"社畜沒有一個是無辜的"},{"pid":"97c97bd2f602acc5caebcc43e62ecd1d0c5d991a","tid":1031391,"uid":59910,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18ccd6fedc0d1a8708d72beb490acb70f647d34a","tid":1031391,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】青協前督導主任、中文大學社工系前兼職講師鄧惠雄被指於2007年任一計劃內的學長（mentor）時，與女學員（mentee）多次發生性行為，學員畢業後曾拒絕繼續保持性關係，惟鄧仍繼續纏擾。女學員向社工註冊局投訴，昨日展開聆